item.description:
Prometheus is an open-source application created for systems monitoring and alerting. The Prometheus server application can produce limited visualizations of data that it collects and stores from Exporters which send it the data. Prometheus and it&rsquo;s Exporters are good for measuring numerical values over time, things such as: Data Storage/Memory Usage, Network Stats, and Process Monitoring.
{{ with .Resources.GetMatch &ldquo;grafana_ex_anon.png&rdquo; }} {{ end }
Prometheus is often paired with the open-source visualization software Grafana which improves the end-user experience by making queries easier and better looking.
